message:
The Sidekiq worker that handles destroying users (DestroyUser) has exhausted its retries. The monitor will recover shortly after it goes off - this does not mean the issue has been resolved and it will require further action (see linked runbook). 

For more information: [Education Incident Runbooks - User Failed to Destroy](https://joinhandshake.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/EPD/pages/865566925/Education+Incident+Runbooks#User-Failed-to-Destroy-in-Production)
